data.description: Welcome to this stunning, newly reimagined home, located within the prestigious 24 hour gated community of Inverness. This elegant home consists of 4 bedrooms 3.5 baths & is situated on a premium lot nestled on a creek/greenbelt, offering comfort & privacy. Step inside through oversized custom metal double front doors and be greeted by spacious open concept living with soaring vaulted ceilings, inlay hard wood floors, & a centerpiece floor to ceiling stone gas fireplace . THIS home will not disappoint. The kitchen is a chef's dream, boasting contemporary white marble countertops & backsplash, Thermador 6 burner double oven range with a griddle, Thermador dishwasher, along with a 3rd oven and warming drawer, Subzero refrigerator, wine chiller and ice maker. A wall of custom double metal doors provide endless natural sunlight to the main living & dining areas, leading to a lavishly landscaped backyard oasis overlooking a custom built heated Keith Zars pool w/water features & hot tub.  The main floor also features a very spacious and private primary suite with oversized windows overlooking the backyard and a spa-like ensuite for you to enjoy with dual vanities, separate tub and walk-in shower, 2 water closets & 1 bidet. Completing the main floor is a second primary bedroom, full bath, laundry & powder room. Upstairs you will find 2 additional bedrooms, 2 walk-in closets, & 1 bath.  A second stairwell will lead you to the office/flex-media room, which could also be used as dual work spaces. Other features of the home include an upgraded lighting package featuring Restoration Hardware lights, Restoration cabinet hardwae and Fanimation champagne/whiskey wood bladed ceiling fans, 4 inch wood shutters, champagne fixtures throughout,& an imported Italian Murano Vessel sink in the powder room. This home also includes a spacious epoxy finished 3 car garage (capable of 5 car garage with lift), charge point electrical vehicle charging station, water softener, and recirculating hot water pump for instant hot water at all interior faucets. Located just minutes to the medical center, shopping, dining, and much more. This home is an absolute must-see!
